cdata.name: Monetha
cdata.desc:
Monetha is a decentralized payment solution built on the Ethereum network. The Monetha solution leveragessmart contract technology to provideadecentralized trust and reputation system in which sellers ratings are attatched to their respective transactions. The solution also enables merchants to accept ETH and Ethereum-based tokens which can be exchanged automatically into fiat currency

MTH is an Ethereum-based token that is used to pay for goods on Monetha. The value of the MTH tokenis based on its underlying assets, properties and/orassociated rights.Monetha tokens also represent percentage share of revenue of Monetha project.
